does it depend on the software?=20

How is it done?=20
specifically, how is an automatic installation of an application across a =
network from a single installing exe done?=20
imagine each computer having the software installed on it would require a =
user name (which may be repeated on all computers) and a unique location =
identifier (ex, the computr login/workstation number, e.g., BB46620). how =
would that be done?=20
is there ever any calculation done for the cost of a sucessful installation=
? for an unsuccessful installation?=20
is it possible to perform an automatic (non-manual) network install to a =
particular room?=20

Tony, he would like to have the answers by 5pm Tuesday night if possible =
can you help him out?.=20
Thanks=20
Tracy=20



